pageContext.claim: “Joe Biden is a globalist who spent forty seven years outsourcing your jobs, opening your borders and sacrificing American blood and treasure on Foreign Wars, you know what they call them, the endless foreign wars, countries that many of you have never heard about....A vote for Biden is a vote to give control of government over to the globalists and communists and socialists and wealthy liberal hypocrites, hypocrites who want to silence, censor,  cancel and punish you.”
pageContext.analysis: This is ridiculous over-the-top rhetoric, a smear on hyperdrive.
